Package: toolero
Title: A Toolkit for Research Workflows
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Erwin", "Lares", , "erwin.lares@wisc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3284-828X"))
Description: Provides utility functions to help researchers implement best
    practices for their coding projects. Includes tools for reading and
    cleaning data files, initializing R projects with a standard folder
    structure, creating 'Quarto' documents from reproducible templates
    with optional sample data and custom styling, detecting the execution
    context across interactive, 'Quarto', and script-based workflows,
    splitting data frames into group-level output files, and rendering
    syntactic tree diagrams as standalone PNG images via 'Typst'.
